<i>adverb</i>: 마땅히 [마땅히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>마땅히 [마땅히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. naturally</dd><br>
<dd>그렇게 하는 것이 옳으므로 당연히.</dd><br>
<dd>Naturally because doing so is a right thing to do.</dd><br>
<dd>2. suitably</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 조건이나 상황에 적당하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Appropriately in a certain condition or situation.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>